        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nSurprised it was in a few of these. Is Xacml jar only needed for Junit testing? Because during runtime the archetype should be calling the PDP API for guard decisions. I know for the template.demo.clc it will need to be there.",
