        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-02-08 20:21:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Surprised it was in a few of these. Is Xacml jar only needed for\n > Junit testing? Because during runtime the archetype should be\n > calling the PDP API for guard decisions. I know for the\n > template.demo.clc it will need to be there.\n\nEverything that uses guards includes the \"guard\" dependency, so should get xacml dependency indirectly.",
        "patchset_number": 2
