        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n> Probably there should also be counterpart changes in the brmsgw\n > source code as they have dependency.json when they put together the\n > artifact, probably that should be changed as well ..\n\nThe exclusion lists in the policy/engine poms should probably be kept in sync.  However, it is not necessary to make any changes to them as a result of this review; the policy/engines poms are independent and policy/engine still builds fine with these changes.",
