        "timestamp": "2019-02-11 16:43:37.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThanks for checking on the zip Jim.\n\nWith regards to policy/engine, this is what I meant:\nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/engine/tree/BRMSGateway/dependency.json\n\nI think there's another one of these dependency.json in the same project, if you search for it, brmsgw goes off from these dependencies to generate the rules jar at runtime.   I think the dependency should be removed from these files too, as it has the guard one.",
